## Summary Table: Pros and Cons of Paying College Athletes

| **Pros**                                          | **Cons**                                           |
|---------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------|
| Provides much-needed income and financial support | Undermines amateurism and educational focus        |
| Compensates for injury risk and time commitment   | Creates budgetary challenges for schools            |
| Motivates athletes and improves performance       | May cause resentment among non-athlete students     |
| Fairer distribution of revenue generated          | Difficult to determine fair pay across sports       |
| Reduces corruption and illicit payments           | Risk of financial mismanagement by athletes         |
| Supports low-income families                        | Changes culture and spirit of college sports        |
| Encourages healthier athletes                       |                                                    |

